TopicTitle: Sector 7 Space Laboratories - Elcano Challenge Report

Articles.Content:
Started my second attempt on the Elcano Challenge because the first wasn't the best idea, it went to file 13. My second attempt is going well and it was started one week ago today. This Challenge has Challenges within itself and you will also fine Kerbin is a very beautiful place the more you travel. I have a few pictures of my journey so far and it's been one heck of a long one. I hope to be finished this weekend. I will give my complete report and reveal my craft that was inspired by my Indy Car (Indy Xtreme) the craft is named after it Indy Xtreme GT (Indy Xtreme Global Transport).
